he sort of searches where Google makes the most money =E2=80=94 travel, ins=
urance, etc. =E2=80=94 may not be well-suited for chat interfaces anyways.

That, though, ought only increase the concern for Google=E2=80=99s manageme=
nt that generative AI may, in the specific context of search, represent a d=
